name: ATI Aquablue Special High-Output T5 Bulb
description: ATI Aquablue Special T5 HO Fluorescent bulb combines the properties of a full-spectrum bulb with an elevated blue color peak producing a bulb with an approximate color temperature of 15000K. Recommended Use: as a stand-alone bulb or in combination with Blue Plus, Purple Plus, True Actinic or other supplemental T5 bulbs.
short_description: A full-spectrum bulb with an approximate color temperature of 15000K
product_name: ATI Aquablue Special High-Output T5 Bulb
product_help_intro1:
Mix & Match pricing for this item is available for
CASE QUANTITIES ONLY.
product_help_intro2:
You must order a COMPLETE CASE of a single item to qualify for the case pricing. You may not combine single units of Mix & Match items to create a case.

For items offering Mix & Match pricing, you may combine COMPLETE CASES of that item with full cases of other available items listed.
product_help_happy:
Example of Qualifying Mix & Match:

+ 60 ATI 24W Coral Plus Bulbs

+ 40 ATI 24W Blue Plus Bulbs

= 100 Units / 10 cases

Qualifies for Mix & Match 10+ Case Pricing!
product_help_unhappy1:
Example of Non-Qualifying Mix & Match:

+ 60 ATI 24W Coral Plus Bulbs

+ 21 ATI 24W Blue Plus Bulbs

+ 19 ATI 80W Blue Plus Bulbs

= 100 Units / 9 cases + 10 units, NOT 10 Cases

Does Not Qualify for Mix & Match 10+ Case Pricing

Qualifies for 1+ Case Pricing
product_help_unhappy2:
Example of Non-Qualifying 1+ Case Pricing:

+ 6 ATI 24W Coral Plus Bulbs

+ 4 ATI 24W Blue Plus Bulbs

= 10 Units, NOT 1 case

Does Not Qualify for 1+ Case Pricing
